little jokes will lead you, son.

01:08.111 --> 01:09.571
Boy: Okay, Dad, I'm...
I'm sorry.

01:09.738 --> 01:11.573
Man: That's all right, son,
you're forgiven.

01:12.031 --> 01:13.575
- Man: Oh, and son?
